{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-304-primonacci","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 304: Primonacci","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za bilo koji pozitivan ceo broj $n$, funkcija $\\text{next_prime}(n)$ vraća najmanji prosti broj $p$ takav da je $p > n$.</p>\n<p>Niz $a(n)$ je definisan kao: $a(1) = \\text{next_prime}({10}^{14})$ i $a(n) = \\text{next_prime}(a(n - 1))$ za $n > 1$.</p>\n<p>Fibonacci niz $f(n)$ definisan je kao: $f(0) = 0$, $f(1) = 1$ i $f(n) = f(n - 1) + f(n - 2)$ za $n > 1$.</p>\n<p>Niz $b(n)$ je definisan kao $f(a(n))$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $\\sum b(n)$ za $1≤n≤100,000$. Navedite svoj odgovor po modulu $1,234,567,891,011$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f49d1000cf542c50ffaf","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301958,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-304-primonacci"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function primonacci() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nprimonacci();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>primonacci()</code> treba da vrati <code>283988410192</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(primonacci(), 283988410192);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-304-primonacci","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-probl